<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><head>(L2) 18 ]•2EtO•MeOH</head><p>In the remaining allocated time for the experiment we were also able to collect a full data set for the high nuclearity cluster of manganese depicted in Figure <ref type="figure">2</ref> (see Scheme 1 for the chemical structure of the ligands). We are still waiting to publish this result due to a combination of several factors, with the most relevant being the need to scale-up the synthesis so the magnetic properties could be studied in detail. </p></div>			</div>
